parameters:
\nc<>What, that movie!? Tornadoes from the sky... sharks...! I
don't understand the meaning!

\nc<>After that, I kept looking around at clothes... I feel like
I might be more tired than fighting villains...

\nc<>That's good then. Oh, would you like a bite of cake? Here,
the milk crepe here is really famous.

\nc<>Senpai, you like sweet things, don't you? Your cheeks are
all puffy like a squirrel. So cute~!

\nc<>It's not cute, right!? What are you taking a picture of!
Hurry up and delete it!

\nc<>But I am a kind underclassman, so if Senpai says to delete
it, I will delete it for them.

\nc<>Well, I already posted it on my SNS account, though.
*laughs*

\nc<>Yes, yes, it's your senpai Reina. Why are you so flustered?
It's just a mere photo.

\nc<>Why... because I can't read the atmosphere... I'm not
cute... and I don't know about popular dramas either...

\nc<？>Kei-chan, so the male lead actor for this drama is... huh?
Ah, you haven't seen it yet.

\nc<？>Haa... Somehow, I can't seem to have a conversation with
Kei.
\nc<>Because I can't even have an interesting conversation...
\nc<>Indeed, Senpai is not the type who is good at talking.

\nc<>But they do pay attention to me, and I don't watch dramas
either!

\nc<>Just because someone has a lot of friends doesn't mean they
watch dramas, you know?
\nc<>Above all, Senpai is really cute! That's the proof!
\nc<>(This is a photo of me that Reina posted...)
\nc<>(Huh, no way. The number of likes is off the charts!?)
\nc<>Just so you know, I'm not Sakura, okay?
\nc<>Okay, okay! I understand! You don't have to read it!
\nc<>But, it is an undeniable fact that I am thought of that way.

\nc<>Senpai should realize their own worth more. Do you
understand?
\nc<>(Uwaaah. I'm so embarrassed, I could die.)
\nc<>(...But, maybe I don't feel that bad...)
\nc<>I obtained the memory R1: Popular Person Experience.
